Information about Adisucipto for english viewers:

Adisucipto or Agustinus Adisucipto is an Indonesian Heroes, which was build a flight school in Yogyakarta (formerly Maguwo Airfield) and one of founder of Infonesia Air Force

He died in action when flew suplies for Indonesian guerillas due Indonesian-Netherland confrontation in 1947.He last rank is air commodore.

For commemorate his service as indonesia hero, Maguwo airfield renamed to Adisucipto Airport, one of international airport in Java.
